Class Forklift

java.lang.Object
  hardwareAbstraction.Forklift

public class Forklift
extends java.lang.Object

Handles movement of claw/grabber & center ultrasonic mechanism up and down.

The following mechanism makes sure the robot only has one state at a time. The robot will only go to different states once.

convertDistanceToAngle

private static int convertDistanceToAngle(int distance)
This method turns a distance into an angle for the spool to turn. Takes as parameter the distance you want to lift. It is essential the radius of spool be calibrated. The radius is the radius of the "spool" the string winds onto. The formula used is: d = 2*pi*radius*(angle)/360 ==> angle = 360 * d / (2*pi*radius).

Parameters:
distance -
Returns:
